Sky's reporter Michael Bridge: &quot;Before the end of last season there were discussions between Palace and Zaha about him potentially playing in the Champions League, something #AFC currently cannot offer.&quot;<br />
<br />
Michael Bridge: &quot;Another key thing is that Zaha signed a new long-term deal at Selhurst Park last season, Palace hold the upper hand after giving him a long-term contract. I am fearing that this could potentially get messy.&rdquo;

Zaha哥哥接受採訪：&ldquo;水晶宮和水晶宮的球迷在Zaha心中永遠佔據著最高的位置，他們的支持對Zaha而言意味著全世界然而...Zaha的夢想是為阿仙奴踢球。&rdquo;<br />
<br />
&ldquo;考慮到Zaha為水晶宮保級付出了一切，我希望水晶宮能和阿仙奴達成轉會協議，實現Zaha為阿仙奴踢歐洲賽事的夢想 - 阿仙奴是他兒時起就支持的球隊。&ldquo;
